race.comment: MEPUNGA LILLY (4) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at Sandown over 515m behind Zipper On Time (29.94) in a Special conditions G2. Placed at her previous run. Can atone. PAW MANNY (3) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, half a length from the winner Paw Xena (25.30) at Ballarat. Can measure up. RED STILETTO (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (34.98) in a Special conditions H at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Form from her last run is proving strong. Should be about the mark. PAW LOUIS (7) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.
